{"tid":399304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"國際小姐王詠珩先係美貌與智慧並重　讚雷莊𠒇處理負評夠大方","createTime":"2017-09-14T00:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T08:13:19.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59e12e44d8bd9a8c19d61f8f9996c77ad9063f40","tid":399304,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T00:00:22.000Z","msg":"近年TVB選完港姐後都會有不少批評聲音，今年奪冠的雷莊𠒇 更被網友鬧到體無完膚，反而令到今年11月準備到東京參加國際小姐的港區代表王詠珩（Wing）亦意外被起底，今年23歲嘅Wing5呎8吋，仲高過今屆冠軍雷莊𠒇 。與Sofia嘅開朗個性截然不同嘅王詠珩（Wing），性格談吐都是比較文靜優雅，廣東話超流利，係真正嘅「港女」。直言無乜自信心嘅佢都話完全無諗過會參加選美，「其實我一係台上就會怯場，我隻手都會不自然咁震嘅嗰種人。雖然細嗰嘅時候，好多auntie uncle都有叫我參加港姐，但細嗰覺得港姐要著bikini，我就覺得好怕醜，所以就無特別諗過去選。」<br />\n<br />\n攝影：黃國立<br />\n場地：Kiz Royal<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833065/xlarge/6367616f5c21c8199787b1bbc8c8a699.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833065%2Fxlarge%2F6367616f5c21c8199787b1bbc8c8a699.jpg&h=232ffc72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王詠珩性格比較文靜優雅，自己都估唔到會參加選美比賽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833422/xlarge/0d60b1dfacaf181926d4af4a8a2da926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833422%2Fxlarge%2F0d60b1dfacaf181926d4af4a8a2da926.jpg&h=d6e0cf26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833423/xlarge/ecbc7ff364bdf812c52f51162155faab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833423%2Fxlarge%2Fecbc7ff364bdf812c52f51162155faab.jpg&h=05071ca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833427/xlarge/5f68e49c5bbcb82ffd29b788788ca796.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833427%2Fxlarge%2F5f68e49c5bbcb82ffd29b788788ca796.jpg&h=dbc5ef6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833428/xlarge/d4b405857a12dda06b44db7e2deacec7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833428%2Fxlarge%2Fd4b405857a12dda06b44db7e2deacec7.jpg&h=8f832ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833425/xlarge/11ae58bdfbcf23bb6e8a04a214bfeb8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833425%2Fxlarge%2F11ae58bdfbcf23bb6e8a04a214bfeb8f.jpg&h=ded413b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833426/xlarge/35fa3b67a2abdfcb4f72db662f89dae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833426%2Fxlarge%2F35fa3b67a2abdfcb4f72db662f89dae4.jpg&h=4a9f6b66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833424/xlarge/f8492a088bc1192f6b1144d841a0238e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833424%2Fxlarge%2Ff8492a088bc1192f6b1144d841a0238e.jpg&h=afc6a702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833437/xlarge/8504b6d028d04ac1e506ae854d5ec99d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833437%2Fxlarge%2F8504b6d028d04ac1e506ae854d5ec99d.jpg&h=2c7fa5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWing表示自己會積極備戰，希望可以在今次國際小姐比賽中為港增光。<br />\n<br />\n講到王詠珩(Wing)今次在國際小姐比賽中雖然代表香港，但風頭似乎被澳門代表麥嘉欣（Sofia）搶去不少，Wing直言與對方感情太好，不會因外界的流言蜚語影響她們。問到今年港姐冠軍的雷莊𠒇罵聲四起，Wing透露都有睇過報導，「我覺得佢現在嘅處理方法更加大方得體，所以我諗負評開始慢慢減退。」<br />\n<br />\nWing重申一次自己雖然無參加港姐，但同樣都是代表香港走向國際，覺得係一個好機會見識外面嘅世界。與出身選美世家嘅Sofia不同，Wing就直言是受曾參加上屆國際先生嘅朋友影響而參選，「自己都無預料到會參加選美,因為有朋友參加國際先生，佢就遞了我張相俾比賽總監，之後就問我有無興趣參加。聽到之後當然有即刻上網search下係咩一回事，睇完資料都覺得幾有趣，所以就咁參加。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833353/xlarge/3fe49d3b35da65790739f4577c19aa2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833353%2Fxlarge%2F3fe49d3b35da65790739f4577c19aa2b.jpg&h=0d831c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與男友感情穩定嘅Wing，不時在Instagram上載合照，好鬼閃！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833403/xlarge/d730b8c652a87c6857d54ded3bfb8038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833403%2Fxlarge%2Fd730b8c652a87c6857d54ded3bfb8038.jpg&h=c9d312db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833411/xlarge/067a59975479dea17103a9986f053b23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833411%2Fxlarge%2F067a59975479dea17103a9986f053b23.jpg&h=08657b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833406/xlarge/455048f5dd92ede69175b3442c45a408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833406%2Fxlarge%2F455048f5dd92ede69175b3442c45a408.jpg&h=e8b8abcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833404/xlarge/556387129a3741e04ed7275aec935665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833404%2Fxlarge%2F556387129a3741e04ed7275aec935665.jpg&h=42a241f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833405/xlarge/5babe6c698625c6854c1222c964f0a99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833405%2Fxlarge%2F5babe6c698625c6854c1222c964f0a99.jpg&h=15c19e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833407/xlarge/ae53c199445d9c70fb650205cfb7929c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833407%2Fxlarge%2Fae53c199445d9c70fb650205cfb7929c.jpg&h=9d7f2a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833408/xlarge/96406190124c1f53f37ef36e04c05268.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833408%2Fxlarge%2F96406190124c1f53f37ef36e04c05268.jpg&h=ea62271e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833410/xlarge/9c4ae0849ab3a67846962e42cb04a10a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833410%2Fxlarge%2F9c4ae0849ab3a67846962e42cb04a10a.jpg&h=6171fbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833409/xlarge/ec452ec2eb5415b9618ad5c3a2e02784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833409%2Fxlarge%2Fec452ec2eb5415b9618ad5c3a2e02784.jpg&h=6e145812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而男友亦非常支持她的決定，Wing在訪問中笑言對方不是傳媒所講的金融才俊，「佢會同我講唔好再講我咁多嘢喇。（有壓力？）佢會覺得點解我會呀有咁嘅稱號，我真係唔係呀，承受唔起呀！但都OK嘅，好哈彩大家都好鍚住我，無論評論同報導都係好正面。」<br />\n<br />\n但最估唔到Wing原來同今屆港姐獲「友誼小姐」嘅張寶欣原來係好姊妹，「其實我地好細嗰係因為有共同朋友而認識，識落之後又好啱傾，之後仲識埋佢家姐張寶兒，而且之後去到英國讀書都有去佢屋企玩。」一位參加港姐，一位就參加國際小姐，如果稍為有點妒忌都會互相眼紅，但呢嗰情況就無在她們身上發生，Wing說，「我地都知道大家參加唔同嘅比賽，反而會互相鼓勵，上個星期我都有係網上投票俾佢，而佢都有叫我加油。」講到張寶欣已經參選完港姐，可以說是鬆一口氣，Wing亦指沒有特別向對方偷師，「因為我地都知道訓練嘅過程大家都好忙，佢返而會問我幾時正式比賽，仲話想過東京支持我。但我同佢講，我吾可以黎見你架，只可以係lobby見你！」"},{"pid":"8cf7770025cafd044ffbe3f8facd1e34c3dcae02","tid":399304,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/833306/xlarge/05fd87def9ad5b8b4887374b08442dbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F833306%2Fxlarge%2F05fd87def9ad5b8b4887374b08442dbf.jpg&h=9f16c9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最估唔到Wing原來同今屆港姐獲「友誼小姐」嘅張寶欣及家姐張寶兒係好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：溫菁莉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/118857/-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%90-%E7%8E%8B%E8%A9%A0%E7%8F%A9%E5%85%88%E4%BF%82%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%8C%E8%88%87%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E4%B8%A6%E9%87%8D-%E8%AE%9A%E9%9B%B7%E8%8E%8A%F0%A0%92%87%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A0%E8%A9%95%E5%A4%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F118857%2F-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E7%258E%258B%25E8%25A9%25A0%25E7%258F%25A9%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BF%2582%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%258C%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E9%2587%258D-%25E8%25AE%259A%25E9%259B%25B7%25E8%258E%258A%25F0%25A0%2592%2587%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9&d=dgkasUF7vKNrZadgfiPNP10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e9e8ea7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/118857/-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%90-%E7%8E%8B%E8%A9%A0%E7%8F%A9%E5%85%88%E4%BF%82%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%8C%E8%88%87%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E4%B8%A6%E9%87%8D-%E8%AE%9A%E9%9B%B7%E8%8E%8A%F0%A0%92%87%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A0%E8%A9%95%E5%A4%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B9</a>"},{"pid":"ebbf1cd178aeea3a8d1757a9b64f483c0a479363","tid":399304,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T00:43:39.000Z","msg":"靚版張秀文"},{"pid":"a8c75719c314457f29785b49c35a20eb0eecc24c","tid":399304,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"呢個堅靚"}]}